<refsect1 role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>
<link linkend="GtkVolumeButton"><type>GtkVolumeButton</type></link> is a subclass of <link linkend="GtkScaleButton"><type>GtkScaleButton</type></link> that has
been tailored for use as a volume control widget with suitable 
icons, tooltips and accessible labels.
</para>
</refsect1>

